{"tid":1019593,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"法拉利時速170公里狂飆　隱形戰車公路拘危駕司機","createTime":"2019-02-13T05:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T10:34:09.000Z","uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"8e158205932a80eeae2ed87d0bed7414dfbd362c","tid":1019593,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"36歲揸架 458 仲要咁撚慢, 抵拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我20歲揸架 CL7 都 keep住180 cut 油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlny 我今日(13日)早上近8時，新界北總區交通部執行及管制組特遣隊人員，進行代號「AIRCHAIN」打擊貨車超載行動，於屯門公路巡邏至深井對開時，發現一輛白色法拉利458超級跑車往屯門方向高速行駛，「隱形戰車」立即尾隨追截，期間超跑在公路上飛馳，多次左穿右插，時速更一度高達170公里狂飆，警員窮追7公里至小欖轉車站終將法拉利截停。<br />\n<br />\n警員向該名姓蔡(36歲)司機調查後，以涉嫌危險駕駛將報稱商人的跑車司機拘捕，更揭發他未交罰款被通緝，蔡被扣查後獲准保釋，須於3月下旬向警方報到，跑車被拖到大欖涌車輛扣留中心以作進一步檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署資料，超速的法拉利跑車於2012年出廠並於同年首次登記，車價逾350萬港元，登記車主為一間公司。<br />\n<br />\n而今早追車經過，被其他車輛的「車Cam」攝入鏡頭，還原涉事法拉利狂飆的情況，據片段顯示，跑車沿中線高速爬頭，越過一輛私家車後切入快線，隨即被「隱形戰車」尾隨閃燈追截。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QrwBSnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrwBSnB.jpg&h=46de3d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGHp1fW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGHp1fW.jpg&h=8ed20610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9aLi5HC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9aLi5HC.jpg&h=d1297356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70gVouh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70gVouh.jpg&h=c9cb470a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8sFru9i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8sFru9i.jpg&h=ee4984f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJcdUAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJcdUAY.jpg&h=3b3208c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80909624e6c86edc5d5cda4f8cdad5420b01200a","tid":1019593,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213081539961-0213_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190213%2Fbkn-20190213081539961-0213_00822_001.html&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=04700b0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213081539961-0213_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有片睇, 仲要係轉車站落斜位, 果個位正常個個都 200+ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9d62f3d3bf5596bf7c6f1034f80b6e3617cbe9","tid":1019593,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾 <br />\n拎公司車黎玩<br />\nbtw 跑車係香港真係無用 170都發揮唔到"},{"pid":"9d310850ca168b8c8427b479ba006add7e567ef5","tid":1019593,"uid":89227,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"5a9d62f3d3bf5596bf7c6f1034f80b6e3617cbe9","tid":1019593,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾 <br />\n拎公司車黎玩<br />\nbtw 跑車係香港真係無用 170都發揮唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"公司持有又垃圾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedb5f4e824bbaef36c05eb29152ecf2fb279189","tid":1019593,"uid":72751,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"quote":{"pid":"5a9d62f3d3bf5596bf7c6f1034f80b6e3617cbe9","tid":1019593,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾 <br />\n拎公司車黎玩<br />\nbtw 跑車係香港真係無用 170都發揮唔到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"你條友真係唔識架wo"},{"pid":"29c87d3b4af06991392bc8597d7b9ac22a68ae17","tid":1019593,"uid":153863,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:52